  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nCOMING SOON\nAI Traffic Analytics\n\nTrack and analyze AI chatbot traffic with precision. Get granular insights into sessions, bounce rates, top-performing pages, and competitors across ChatGPT, Perplexity, AI Mode, Gemini, Claude, and more\n\nStart free trial\nRequest a demo\n\nNo credit card required\n\nCombine your AI chatbot traffic statistics and visibility metrics\n\nSee how much traffic LLM-powered systems send to your site and track visibility across them\n\nGA4-based AI chatbot traffic analysis\nAI visibility and performance tracking\nGA4-based AI chatbot traffic analysis\n\nGet real GA4 data on AI chatbot sessions, users, bounce rate, and more. All segmented by sources like ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, and more, and visualized through clear charts and graphs.\n\nStart free trial\nBuild your AI search strategy on solid data\n\nUse precise traffic and visibility data to understand what works, where to improve, and how to outperform the competition with our AI chatbot traffic tool\n\nAnalyze AI session quality\n\nSee how AI-referred users behave on your site. Track bounce rate, events, sessions, and more. Fine-tune your strategy based on real user behavior.\n\nReview landing page performance\n\nIdentify pages linked by AI chatbots and analyze how users interact with them. Use these insights to prioritize and optimize your pages.\n\nCompare traffic by AI source\n\nBreak down your traffic by AI chatbot and view the platforms driving the most sessions, engagement, and events to better allocate your efforts.\n\nResearch competitor visibility\n\nTrack how your competitors perform in AI responses. Monitor their visibility, links, and mentions to find missed opportunities and growth potential.\n\nStart free trial\nСomplete analytics set to understand your AI chatbot traffic\n\nAccess segmented traffic reports, monitor shifts, and fine-tune your strategy b",
